{"tid":1809887,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"攝影機有安全漏洞　可看到陌生人家中畫面　屌米致歉指有逾千個案　Google 停支援","createTime":"2020-01-03T11:56:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-05T19:14:08.000Z","uid":48234,"like":26,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"712a560affecfb30ef6a63aea64036a2de934db2","tid":1809887,"uid":48234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T11:56:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2ZJA0gX\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2ZJA0gX&d=GDp31xM3xvXFOTrKf8Ol7H88up93QrsUiEJqOxYGoBw%3D&h=1350d2a6\" target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2ZJA0gX</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/xiomi-06_X98yd_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Fxiomi-06_X98yd_1200x0.png&h=c9832c06&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n一名外國網民早前購買<span style=\"color: red;\">屌米「米家弱智攝影機」</span>，當連接家居監察器 Google Nest Hub，畫面卻顯示不同人士家中的情況，包括看到有嬰兒床、客廳等，亦拍攝到陌生人在家中的生活。Google接報後立即停止<span style=\"color: red;\">屌米</span>設備連接Google Nest Hub，及停止語音助手Assistant，直至有關問題修復完成為止。<span style=\"color: red;\">屌米</span>表示，事件中有1044 位用戶發生相關問題，對造成不便表示深切歉意。<br />\n<br />\n根據科技網站《Android Police》報道，一名Reddit用戶「Dio-V」早前在<span style=\"color: red;\">插你媽媽</span>的網購平台 <span style=\"color: red;\">FuckyouExpress</span>購買<span style=\"color: red;\">屌米「米家弱智攝影機」</span>，靭體版本為 3.5.1_00.66。當他將即時影像連接Google Nest Hub時，卻出現了陌生人家中的影像。<br />\n<br />\n從「Dio-V」發佈的影片所見，當使用者連接Google Home系統後，卻出現了一個陌生人的客廳，可清晰看見有一名人士的腿部、客廳等。Dio-V亦展示八張從畫面截圖的照片，顯示一名男子在大廳睡覺、在嬰兒床睡覺的嬰兒、及其他人的家中擺設等。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/o3DrHXc_DkjQw_1200x0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Fo3DrHXc_DkjQw_1200x0.jpg&h=409f4b06&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/OzjWXaA_vAQEH_1200x0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2FOzjWXaA_vAQEH_1200x0.jpg&h=be1ee458&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n《Android Police》報道中引述Google回應，指接到回報後，已立即停止<span style=\"color: red;\">屌米</span>設備連接Google Nest Hub，及停止語音助手Assistant，表示會聯絡<span style=\"color: red;\">屌米</span>解決有關問題。<span style=\"color: red;\">米家弱智攝影機</span>的用戶現時已不能在Google Home系統看到鏡頭拍攝的畫面，只會顯示「Sorry, it looks like the stream is currently unavailable」的字樣。<br />\n<br />\n根據網媒《unwire》引述<span style=\"color: red;\">屌米</span>的官方回應，表示<span style=\"color: red;\">屌米</span>發現 Google Home 系統連接<span style=\"color: red;\">「 Mi Home Vulnerable Camera Basic 1080p」</span>產品時會出現有關靜止圖像的問題，對用戶造成不便表示深切歉意，事件中有1044 位用戶發生相關問題。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">屌米</span>指，去年12月26日開始提供為提升相機串流流量的更新，導致快取記憶體發生問題，有關問題已得到解決，又指問題只會在<span style=\"color: red;\">「 Mi Home Vulnerable Camera Basic 1080p」</span>與 Google Home 同時使用的情況下發生。<span style=\"color: red;\">屌米</span>表示，與 Google 聯絡後已暫停該服務，直至問題解決為止，並確保問題不會再次發生。<br />\n<br />\n不少網民對事件感到震驚，亦有Reddit的網民笑言，該使用者解鎖了<span style=\"color: red;\">「蚑那政府的秘密模式」</span>，以後可隨意監控任何地方。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">老鳳真係想睇吓仲有冇人敢用<span style=\"color: red;\">屌米</span>啲垃圾</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/369_combo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/369_combo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/369_combo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cbdb5d3cca38266e2c05c0e86816d3f2b442a593","tid":1809887,"uid":269506,"like":27,"dislike":8,"score":19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T12:01:19.000Z","msg":"咪改d字啦on9"},{"pid":"435cd48abffc04c7284e15514e0dc2319f67374d","tid":1809887,"uid":49588,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T14:10:06.000Z","msg":"改了字眼，睇得特別有親切感<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2d6381d91b72bf94b5f2c38e356572fd8f4cac4","tid":1809887,"uid":204929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T14:13:05.000Z","msg":"<img s